A man has been killed and three others injured when a light motor vehicle collided with a taxi on Long Market and Retief Road intersection in Pietermaritzburg CBD on Monday.&#8220;On arrival, paramedics found the body of a man lying near his light motor vehicle, he was assessed on the scene and sadly there was nothing that the paramedics could do as he was declared dead,&#8221; said Arrive Alive.Three other men were found on the scene with minor injuries. They were treated and transported to Northdale Hospital for further treatment.The cause of the accident is yet unknown.-TNA Reporter 